cs.CV, cs.GR, cs.LG, cs.MM, cs.AI 

This paper deals with image restoration and segmentation tasks, which are typically studied in the computer vision (cs.CV) and graphics (cs.GR) sub-categories. The paper also introduces a novel dataset and uses deep learning techniques, which are common in the machine learning (cs.LG) and multimedia (cs.MM) sub-categories. Finally, the paper involves semantic segmentation, which is a task often studied in the artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-category.
